Key Match Events: Youssef En Nesyri scored a brace for Morocco
Boufal also scored a brace for Morocco
Miscellaneous Highlights: This is the first meeting between Morocco and Sierra Leone since June 2003
The match was played as part of training and will not be broadcast
Others: The match was played at the Laurent Pokou Stadium in San Pédro, Côte d'Ivoire
The stadium has a capacity of 20,000 spectators
